  <p>Nothing in these terms excludes liability that cannot lawfully be excluded. Mandatory consumer protections remain unaffected where they apply.</p>

  <h2>11. Suspension and termination</h2>
  <p>You may stop using the website and revoke authorization at any time. We may restrict access to the website or OAuth client when reasonably necessary to address abuse, security incidents, provider requirements, legal obligations, or material violations of these terms.</p>

  <h2>12. Changes and contact</h2>
  <p>We may update these terms as AgentWeave or its provider integrations change. The effective date above identifies the current version. Continued use after an update means the updated terms apply to later use.</p>
  <p>Questions about these terms may be sent to <a href={`mailto:${contactEmail}`}>{contactEmail}</a>.</p>
